Android 3.0 Animation, a Beginner's Guide
Chapter 1 Example Application
Counting Calculator

Author: Alex Shaw
Publisher: Packt Publishing

Eclipse installation instructions:

1.  Unzip this folder to a location on your hard disk
2.  In Eclipse, select Import... from the File menu
3.  Select "Existing Projects Into Workspace"
4.  Set the location of this folder as the root directory
5.  Click Finish 